Allow me to reintroduce myself…

My name is Dream. I have a reputation of being the most dependable person in a lot of people’s lives. I have a lot of outstanding qualities but none of us are perfect. We take on others projections of us and attach it to our identities. Today is the day you expel that and define yourself. If you’re reading this reintroduce yourself in the comments.

Wealth is of the 💓 and 🧠, not the pocket 💰

Being rich is not the goal! To make a living through my purpose is what I strive for. Last year I stared death in the face surviving 3 vehicular accidents. 

Whatever the divine powers may be it wasn’t my time to leave this Earth. Through everything else I just want to see the people I care about truly thrive! Life is a gift we should treasure. If you have someone you only want the best for in your life, let them know or feel free to tag them. 

Love,
Dream
